Description: Up for grabs is a 2015 Squier Tele for Tele fans on a budget! Vintage 50's style and feel.. this one won't last long. This guitar is used and shows a few signs of wear. There are a few dings, one on the diewall and one on the headstock. Pickguard has been swapped out for a white one and control knobs have been swapped out for wooden ones. See pics for full cosmetic details. Serialized  cgs1509337 8lbs 10oz No case included A CLASSIC WITHIN YOUR BUDGET Squier's Classic Vibe Telecaster® '50s puts classic "blackguard" Telecaster vibe into a gorgeous Vintage Blonde-finished pine-body guitar with authentic Telecaster tone. You'll be hard-pressed to tell whether or not you are holding a premium ash-body instrument when you pick up this sweet-sounding guitar and unleash its spectacular sound.
